environment variable must also include the directory of the OS/2
.fi DOSCALLS.LIB
file which is usually
.fi &pc.OS2.
.if '&lang' eq 'C' or '&lang' eq 'C/C++' .do begin
The
.ev LIBOS2
environment variable must also include the location of the &prod16
math library files.
